09:41.289 --> 09:44.418
called me "Ewey Dewey."

09:44.459 --> 09:45.668
This is the same girl who puts

09:45.710 --> 09:47.628
paste in your hair

09:45.710 --> 09:47.628
all the time, isn't it?

09:47.670 --> 09:49.630
Mm-hmm, well,

09:47.670 --> 09:49.630
you know, she's just

09:47.670 --> 09:49.630
doing this because

09:49.672 --> 09:52.592
she likes you. It's her way

09:49.672 --> 09:52.592
of getting your attention.

09:53.676 --> 09:55.636
So she doesn't think I'm ewey?

09:55.678 --> 09:57.347
No, of course not.

09:59.349 --> 10:01.268
He's right.

09:59.349 --> 10:01.268
Hmm.

10:01.309 --> 10:03.103
Hey, Dad?

10:01.309 --> 10:03.103
Hmm.

10:03.144 --> 10:04.812
I have a little situation that

10:03.144 --> 10:04.812
maybe you can help me out with.

10:04.854 --> 10:05.688
There's this girl who's...

10:04.854 --> 10:05.688
I suggest

10:05.730 --> 10:06.940
that you leave her alone

10:06.981 --> 10:08.649
before she calls

10:06.981 --> 10:08.649
the police on you.

10:09.692 --> 10:11.486
Okay, thanks.

10:12.404 --> 10:14.448
What's wrong?

10:14.489 --> 10:15.698
What do you mean?

10:15.740 --> 10:18.118
Well, I noticed you

10:15.740 --> 10:18.118
looking at me.

10:18.159 --> 10:19.660
Nothing.

10:19.702 --> 10:22.122
See? It's creepy.

10:22.163 --> 10:24.082
You know, Hal,

10:22.163 --> 10:24.082
I got to admit it.

10:24.124 --> 10:25.917
Not working

10:24.124 --> 10:25.917
has really been good for you.

10:25.959 --> 10:27.502
You seem so much happier,

10:27.544 --> 10:29.670
so much more attentive,

10:27.544 --> 10:29.670
tuned in to the boys.

10:41.724 --> 10:43.977
Hal...

10:44.018 --> 10:45.728
My God, you're beautiful.

11:08.751 --> 11:11.712
CRAIG:

11:08.751 --> 11:11.712
Okay, team,

11:08.751 --> 11:11.712
you did a great job yesterday.

11:11.754 --> 11:14.090
Unfortunately,

11:11.754 --> 11:14.090
I lost all the numbers.

11:14.132 --> 11:17.552
I think I accidentally

11:14.132 --> 11:17.552
mailed them to my mom.

11:17.594 --> 11:18.428
(all groaning)

11:18.470 --> 11:19.804
Yeah, so... whoops.

11:19.846 --> 11:21.806
So why don't you guys

11:19.846 --> 11:21.806
start recounting?

11:21.848 --> 11:23.933
I'm going to head

11:21.848 --> 11:23.933
to the downtown store

11:23.975 --> 11:26.978
and play a little "defense,"

11:23.975 --> 11:26.978
if you know what I'm saying.

11:27.020 --> 11:29.648
Uh... Garkech,

11:27.020 --> 11:29.648
you're in charge.

11:29.730 --> 11:31.983
Whoa, whoa, whoa...

11:29.730 --> 11:31.983
you're putting him in charge?

11:32.025 --> 11:33.527
He doesn't speak English.

11:33.568 --> 11:35.736
We don't even know

11:33.568 --> 11:35.736
if Garkech is really his name.

11:35.778 --> 11:37.738
We don't know that it's not.

11:37.780 --> 11:39.740
Besides, he hasn't questioned

11:37.780 --> 11:39.740
every decision I've made.

11:39.782 --> 11:41.742
That's because he can't.

11:41.784 --> 11:43.244
And what happened

11:41.784 --> 11:43.244
to our lunch break?

11:43.286 --> 11:44.663
CRAIG:

11:43.286 --> 11:44.663
I can't hear you.

11:44.703 --> 11:46.747
Thought you might be

11:44.703 --> 11:46.747
ready for some aspirin.

11:46.789 --> 11:48.749
I'm working for a moron.

11:48.791 --> 11:49.750
Of course you are, honey.

11:49.792 --> 11:51.127
Your boss is an idiot,

11:51.169 --> 11:52.753
your coworkers

11:51.169 --> 11:52.753
are incompetent,

11:52.795 --> 11:54.381
and you are

11:52.795 --> 11:54.381
underappreciated.

11:54.422 --> 11:55.923
Welcome to the

11:54.422 --> 11:55.923
working world.

11:55.965 --> 11:57.758
How do people do it?

11:57.800 --> 11:59.260
Well, let's see...

11:59.302 --> 12:00.761
If you want to eat,

11:59.302 --> 12:00.761
sleep indoors,

12:00.803 --> 12:02.597
you know,

12:00.803 --> 12:02.597
those kinds of luxuries,

12:02.639 --> 12:04.349
you really don't have

12:02.639 --> 12:04.349
much of a choice.

12:04.391 --> 12:06.434
What about Dad?

12:04.391 --> 12:06.434
He had a choice.

12:06.476 --> 12:09.020
Every 20 years,

12:06.476 --> 12:09.020
you're allowed a

12:06.476 --> 12:09.020
two-week breakdown.

12:09.062 --> 12:10.938
Oh, I can't wait.

12:10.980 --> 12:13.358
(whispering)

12:13.400 --> 12:16.069
He says, "Get back to work!"

12:16.110 --> 12:17.696
I really appreciate

12:17.736 --> 12:19.822
your letting me take

12:17.736 --> 12:19.822
this vocational exam.

12:19.864 --> 12:21.782
I know it's generally

12:19.864 --> 12:21.782
for older kids.

12:21.824 --> 12:24.285
I just felt like

12:21.824 --> 12:24.285
I really needed some help.

12:24.327 --> 12:26.454
I don't want to make

12:24.327 --> 12:26.454
a wrong decision.

12:26.496 --> 12:29.416
Well... did you get

12:26.496 --> 12:29.416
the test results?

12:29.457 --> 12:30.791
Oh, yes.

12:30.833 --> 12:32.793
What did they say I should do?

12:32.835 --> 12:35.796
Well... according to this...

12:35.838 --> 12:38.258
absolutely anything you want.

12:38.299 --> 12:39.426
What?

12:39.467 --> 12:40.719
Yeah, you-you scored

12:40.759 --> 12:42.512
equally excellent in all areas.

12:42.554 --> 12:43.804
According

12:42.554 --> 12:43.804
to this test,

12:43.846 --> 12:46.057
there isn't a career

12:43.846 --> 12:46.057
on the planet

12:46.099 --> 12:47.267
you wouldn't be great at.

12:47.308 --> 12:49.102
Congratulations.

12:49.143 --> 12:52.188
Well, that... that doesn't

12:49.143 --> 12:52.188
exactly clarify anything.

12:52.230 --> 12:53.856
I-I was kind of hoping...

12:53.898 --> 12:55.816
You know, kid,

12:53.898 --> 12:55.816
there are a lot of people

12:55.858 --> 12:58.486
who would kill to have

12:55.858 --> 12:58.486
both "professional golfer"

12:58.528 --> 13:00.697
and "neurosurgeon"

12:58.528 --> 13:00.697
on their test results.

13:00.739 --> 13:02.532
Yeah, but that doesn't help me.

13:02.574 --> 13:04.200
I mean,

13:02.574 --> 13:04.200
how am I supposed to decide

13:04.242 --> 13:06.202
if I don't have

13:04.242 --> 13:06.202
any parameters at all?

13:06.244 --> 13:08.829
Well, boo-hoo for you,

13:06.244 --> 13:08.829
Mr. Unlimited Potential.

13:08.871 --> 13:11.832
Let me wipe my tears for you

13:08.871 --> 13:11.832
on my plastic briefcase.

13:11.874 --> 13:14.335
Does the test at least say

13:11.874 --> 13:14.335
what I might like?

13:14.377 --> 13:16.421
Aside from exposing

13:14.377 --> 13:16.421
middle-aged underachievers

13:16.463 --> 13:17.880
for the failures they are?

13:17.922 --> 13:19.006
Nope.

13:19.048 --> 13:20.550
Can I take the test again?

13:20.592 --> 13:22.093
Uh... no.

13:22.135 --> 13:23.470
Now, if you'll

13:22.135 --> 13:23.470
excuse me,

13:23.511 --> 13:24.845
I have to catch a bus

13:24.887 --> 13:27.223
or I'll be late

13:24.887 --> 13:27.223
for my night job...

13:27.265 --> 13:29.892
unless, of course,

13:27.265 --> 13:29.892
you'd like that, too.

