14:23.863 --> 14:25.948
Dad, what are you doing up?

14:23.863 --> 14:25.948
It's, like, 5:30 in the morning.

14:25.990 --> 14:27.701
Ooh, wow. Really? 5:30?

14:27.742 --> 14:29.369
Yeah, I should be getting

14:27.742 --> 14:29.369
to bed. What are you doing up?

14:29.410 --> 14:30.911
I'm going to work.

14:29.410 --> 14:30.911
Maybe you remember it.

14:30.953 --> 14:32.622
Oh, hey, Francis,

14:30.953 --> 14:32.622
can I borrow 20 bucks?

14:32.664 --> 14:34.123
I need to buy

14:32.664 --> 14:34.123
some more paint.

14:34.165 --> 14:35.542
What? You just bought, like,

14:34.165 --> 14:35.542
six cans of paint yesterday.

14:35.583 --> 14:36.917
What happened to that?

14:36.959 --> 14:39.337
I used it. Man, what are you

14:36.959 --> 14:39.337
grilling me for?

14:39.379 --> 14:41.172
How can you use

14:39.379 --> 14:41.172
six cans of paint

14:39.379 --> 14:41.172
in one day?

14:41.214 --> 14:42.923
Francis, please,

14:41.214 --> 14:42.923
I really need it.

14:42.965 --> 14:44.175
I'm so close.

14:44.217 --> 14:46.093
It's almost right.

14:46.135 --> 14:49.597
Do you have any idea

14:46.135 --> 14:49.597
how hard I have to

14:46.135 --> 14:49.597
work to make $20?

14:49.639 --> 14:51.140
All right. All right!

14:51.182 --> 14:53.351
I didn't ask for a lecture.

15:01.359 --> 15:03.778
Hey, Dad, can

15:01.359 --> 15:03.778
we ask you for

15:01.359 --> 15:03.778
some advice?

15:03.820 --> 15:05.739
The girl who's

15:03.820 --> 15:05.739
been bugging Dewey

15:05.780 --> 15:07.407
still won't

15:05.780 --> 15:07.407
leave him alone.

15:07.448 --> 15:09.950
Now she's calling

15:07.448 --> 15:09.950
me Dewey Dwarf.

15:09.992 --> 15:12.537
I told him-- you've got

15:09.992 --> 15:12.537
to fight fire with fire

15:12.579 --> 15:15.206
and he should come up with some

15:12.579 --> 15:15.206
really raunchy nickname for her

15:15.248 --> 15:17.542
and spread it around school

15:15.248 --> 15:17.542
and church and stuff.

15:17.584 --> 15:19.460
You know,

15:17.584 --> 15:19.460
really get it out there.

15:19.502 --> 15:22.756
Uh, yeah, good

15:19.502 --> 15:22.756
for you, boys.

15:22.797 --> 15:23.964
So the name thing?

15:24.006 --> 15:25.174
You're on board

15:24.006 --> 15:25.174
with that?

15:30.638 --> 15:31.972
All right,

15:30.638 --> 15:31.972
let's get to work.

15:32.014 --> 15:33.600
What's that

15:32.014 --> 15:33.600
girl's name again?

15:33.641 --> 15:36.269
Regina Tucker.

15:36.310 --> 15:39.647
Don't worry.

15:36.310 --> 15:39.647
We'll think

15:36.310 --> 15:39.647
of something.

15:43.025 --> 15:44.944
Another day of crap.

15:46.446 --> 15:47.988
Damn catalogs.

15:50.116 --> 15:51.910
Idiot foreman.

15:51.951 --> 15:54.036
(bus pulls up)

15:59.333 --> 16:01.210
Watch your step.

16:01.252 --> 16:02.670
Whatever.

16:09.928 --> 16:11.971
So tired.

16:21.105 --> 16:24.066
(gasping and panting)

16:35.745 --> 16:39.833
(anguished cry)

16:39.874 --> 16:41.292
Hal, it's past midnight.

16:41.334 --> 16:42.877
Are you coming to bed?

16:42.919 --> 16:44.253
No! How can I go to bed?

16:44.295 --> 16:46.213
It's nothing

16:44.295 --> 16:46.213
what it should be.

16:46.255 --> 16:48.508
Honey, this

16:46.255 --> 16:48.508
is your dream.

16:48.549 --> 16:50.718
It's supposed to be fun.

16:50.760 --> 16:53.053
What are you talking about, fun?

16:53.095 --> 16:54.305
This isn't fun.

16:54.347 --> 16:56.140
This is driving me crazy!

16:56.182 --> 16:58.518
I just... I-I-I

16:56.182 --> 16:58.518
can't get it right.

16:58.559 --> 17:00.687
Well, you don't have

16:58.559 --> 17:00.687
to finish it.

17:00.728 --> 17:03.147
Look at you!

17:00.728 --> 17:03.147
You're killing yourself.

17:03.189 --> 17:04.732
One more day. That's all.

17:04.774 --> 17:06.108
I just need one more day!

17:06.150 --> 17:08.068
(paint cans clattering)

17:08.110 --> 17:11.489
Hal, there has got to be, like,

17:08.110 --> 17:11.489
500 gallons of paint up there.

17:11.531 --> 17:13.574
There isn't...

17:13.616 --> 17:16.243
Yeah, that's about right.

17:16.285 --> 17:19.873
Well... it's over.

17:19.914 --> 17:21.457
I just got the word.

17:21.499 --> 17:23.001
Downtown finished

17:21.499 --> 17:23.001
their inventory.

17:23.042 --> 17:24.293
We've lost.

17:24.335 --> 17:26.587
Chelooz marak!

17:26.629 --> 17:29.298
I think Garkech speaks

17:26.629 --> 17:29.298
for all of us.

17:29.340 --> 17:31.801
I'll be in the cookie aisle.

17:31.843 --> 17:33.093
Well, I say we

17:31.843 --> 17:33.093
just make up

17:33.135 --> 17:35.095
the rest of the

17:33.135 --> 17:35.095
numbers and go home.

17:35.137 --> 17:37.181
Wait a minute, go home?

17:37.223 --> 17:39.934
Weren't you listening? We lost.

17:39.976 --> 17:42.102
I just spent

17:39.976 --> 17:42.102
my entire spring break

17:42.144 --> 17:44.355
counting flip-flops and Vagisil.

17:44.397 --> 17:46.774
You're saying

17:44.397 --> 17:46.774
that was all for nothing?

17:46.816 --> 17:48.317
Yes.

17:48.359 --> 17:51.111
Do you know how many parties

17:48.359 --> 17:51.111
I missed this week?

17:51.153 --> 17:54.490
How many spring break

17:51.153 --> 17:54.490
debaucheries I could've been at?

17:54.532 --> 17:57.618
How many drunken sorority girls

17:54.532 --> 17:57.618
ripped their tops off

17:57.660 --> 18:00.120
without me there

17:57.660 --> 18:00.120
to yell encouragement?

18:00.162 --> 18:02.206
You can't tell me

18:00.162 --> 18:02.206
that was for nothing!

18:02.248 --> 18:05.125
We can't quit!

18:05.167 --> 18:08.504
Come on, guys.

18:05.167 --> 18:08.504
We took on a challenge.

18:08.546 --> 18:12.216
I'm staying until

18:08.546 --> 18:12.216
this is done the right way.

18:12.258 --> 18:14.093
Who's with me?

18:15.386 --> 18:17.137
Why aren't you translating?

18:17.179 --> 18:19.766
There's no point,

18:17.179 --> 18:19.766
but please go on.

18:19.807 --> 18:21.141
That's it.

18:21.183 --> 18:22.142
Ah.

18:22.184 --> 18:23.561
Okay, see you.

18:25.688 --> 18:28.148
All right, now,

18:25.688 --> 18:28.148
keep them closed.

18:28.190 --> 18:30.026
Come on.

18:30.068 --> 18:31.736
You've all been very patient.

18:31.778 --> 18:34.154
I appreciate that.

18:34.196 --> 18:36.032
You've been waiting

18:34.196 --> 18:36.032
a long time, so...

18:36.991 --> 18:38.117
Here it is.

18:42.705 --> 18:44.415
It's...

18:44.457 --> 18:47.752
Yeah.

18:47.794 --> 18:49.169
You're finished?

18:49.211 --> 18:50.838
Yeah. It's perfect!

18:50.880 --> 18:53.758
I mean, it's exactly

18:50.880 --> 18:53.758
how I imagined it.

18:53.800 --> 18:56.343
Then... look at it.

18:56.385 --> 18:57.470
What?

18:57.511 --> 18:58.763
Look at your painting.

18:58.805 --> 19:00.347
Oh, I can see it.

19:00.389 --> 19:02.600
Hal, I want you

19:00.389 --> 19:02.600
to look at that painting

19:02.642 --> 19:05.144
and tell me

19:02.642 --> 19:05.144
that you're satisfied with it.

19:09.899 --> 19:10.900
(yells in frustration)

19:10.942 --> 19:13.193
I knew it! You are not finished.

19:13.235 --> 19:14.403
I can't do it, Lois.

19:14.445 --> 19:15.655
It is driving me crazy.

19:15.696 --> 19:17.197
I have been

19:15.696 --> 19:17.197
slapping on paint

19:17.239 --> 19:19.117
day after day

19:17.239 --> 19:19.117
and I've got nothing!

19:19.158 --> 19:21.035
And I'm never going

19:19.158 --> 19:21.035
to get it right

19:21.077 --> 19:22.662
so I might as well

19:21.077 --> 19:22.662
just forget it.

19:22.703 --> 19:24.204
Oh, you listen to me, Hal.

19:24.246 --> 19:26.040
You are not going back to work

19:26.082 --> 19:27.875
until you get this

19:26.082 --> 19:27.875
out of your system.

19:27.917 --> 19:29.085
No!

19:29.127 --> 19:30.670
You don't

19:29.127 --> 19:30.670
understand.

19:30.711 --> 19:32.212
It is no use!

19:32.254 --> 19:33.714
You are not giving up.

19:33.756 --> 19:36.383
You are going to stay right here

19:33.756 --> 19:36.383
until you are finished.

19:36.425 --> 19:37.802
Oh-ho-ho-ho!

19:37.844 --> 19:39.846
I'm not going to go through this

19:37.844 --> 19:39.846
every five years

19:39.887 --> 19:41.263
when you decide

19:39.887 --> 19:41.263
that there's

19:39.887 --> 19:41.263
a sculpture

19:41.305 --> 19:42.723
or a fountain

19:41.305 --> 19:42.723
or God knows what

19:42.765 --> 19:44.224
it is you still

19:42.765 --> 19:44.224
have to build.

19:44.266 --> 19:45.225
You are going

19:44.266 --> 19:45.225
to finish it!

19:45.267 --> 19:46.644
Fine! You want them

19:46.686 --> 19:48.228
to see me finish it,

19:46.686 --> 19:48.228
I'll finish it.

19:48.270 --> 19:50.272
I'll put a little bit here, huh?

19:50.314 --> 19:52.025
How about there?

19:50.314 --> 19:52.025
How about there?!

19:52.066 --> 19:54.276
And...

19:54.318 --> 19:57.030
Oh... oh...

19:57.071 --> 20:00.116
And...

20:00.158 --> 20:01.534
here...

20:02.869 --> 20:04.871
And...

20:09.083 --> 20:11.502
Awesome!

20:11.544 --> 20:13.629
I don't believe it.

20:13.671 --> 20:17.675
That's it.

20:13.671 --> 20:17.675
That's what was in my head.

20:17.717 --> 20:19.343
FRANCIS:

20:17.717 --> 20:19.343
I've had it!

20:19.385 --> 20:23.263
Everyone at that place are

20:19.385 --> 20:23.263
a bunch of slacker, lazy...

20:23.305 --> 20:26.100
Oh, wow...

20:26.142 --> 20:27.518
Wow!

20:27.560 --> 20:33.273
Hal, I am so proud of you.

20:33.315 --> 20:35.902
I did it.

20:35.943 --> 20:37.987
I really did it.

20:38.029 --> 20:40.156
(ripping sound)

20:40.198 --> 20:41.824
What's that sound?

20:43.367 --> 20:44.284
I don't know.

20:44.326 --> 20:45.536
It sounds like...

20:48.915 --> 20:51.084
Look out! Paint-alanche!

20:51.125 --> 20:53.711
LOIS: Hal!

20:51.125 --> 20:53.711
(Hal yelling)

20:56.005 --> 20:59.592
(muffled):

20:56.005 --> 20:59.592
Mime mokay! Mime mokay!

21:01.343 --> 21:02.553
Oh, honey,

21:01.343 --> 21:02.553
I got to go. Bye.

21:02.595 --> 21:04.764
Francis, come on, I'll drive you

21:02.595 --> 21:04.764
to the bus station.

21:04.805 --> 21:06.306
Hey, vacation's over, mister.

21:06.348 --> 21:08.308
Time to get

21:06.348 --> 21:08.308
back to the old

21:06.348 --> 21:08.308
grindstone. Let's go.

21:08.350 --> 21:10.310
(Francis groaning)

21:10.352 --> 21:12.312
You know,

21:10.352 --> 21:12.312
all this made me realize,

21:12.354 --> 21:14.774
why plan for my future

21:12.354 --> 21:14.774
when it's just going to end up

21:14.815 --> 21:16.817
with a giant wall of paint

21:14.815 --> 21:16.817
crashing down on me?

21:16.859 --> 21:20.780
I'm just going to enjoy

21:16.859 --> 21:20.780
being a kid for a while.

21:20.821 --> 21:23.365
There's a lot

21:20.821 --> 21:23.365
